summary: An ordinance authorizing and directing the Mayor and City Comptroller, for the consideration of One Dollar ($1.00), to execute a quit-claim deed to the County of King, to the easterly 20 feet of Lot 24, Interurban Addition to Seattle, being a 20 foot strip of land lying westerly of and contiguous to the westerly margin of River Street in said addition for public road and high way purposes.
